flowchart TD
    START([CriticAgent 开始]) --> INPUT[读取 VisualSpec + Prompt + output_path]
    INPUT --> RULE[规则评估 Evaluator]
    RULE --> SCORES[五维评分 0-100]
    SCORES --> RISK[风险词检测 risk_count]
    RISK --> OVERALL["overall_score = mean(scores) - risk×2"]
    OVERALL --> LLM{LLM_PROVIDER != mock?}
    LLM -->|是| ENHANCE[LLM 补充 comments/suggestions]
    LLM -->|否| REPORT[生成 EvaluationReport]
    ENHANCE --> REPORT
    REPORT --> THRESHOLD{overall_score < 85?}
    THRESHOLD -->|是且 enable_revision| REV[RevisionAgent 修订 Prompt]
    THRESHOLD -->|否| DONE([完成评估])
    REV --> REGEN[重新生成资产]
    REGEN --> REEVAL[重新评估]
    REEVAL --> DONE
